\section{Running external program}
Create a GC-windows file:
\shellcmd{
abfreqtools.py GC-w 50 hg19.fa > hg19.gc50Base.txt.gz
}

Merging two pileup (from \texttt{samtools}) to obtainf alleles and mutation frequency.
\shellcmd{
abfreqtools.py pileup2tab -gc hg19.gc50Base.txt.gz -r 0001-normal\_blood.pileup.gz -s 0001-met2.pileup.gz -q 20 -n 10 -o 0001-met1.allelesfreq.txt.gz
}

